{"tid":141493,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同男朋友嘈交，佢鬧我賤貨，好難受","createTime":"2017-03-03T03:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T09:15:45.000Z","uid":60491,"like":4,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3edb549e1caf9afaf8398f2e910b5068de611f84","tid":141493,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T03:18:57.000Z","msg":"之前我都拍過幾次拖，亦都有試過同ex發生關係，去到呢個男朋友，佢好似好介意我呢樣嘢。雖然佢對我好個陣真係好好，但一去到有咩野嘈交果陣，佢就三句唔埋兩句就鬧我「賤貨」，話我「cheap精」。<br />\n<br />\n好多次我都覺得好難受好委屈，甚至試過講分手，但每次佢都會係咁chur返我復合，同埋佢同我阿媽關係好好，所以我阿媽都會寧願幫佢唔幫我。我阿媽成日話我唔忍得，小小嘈交就講分手，乜真係我有問題咩？"},{"pid":"710ba9601abedfc3327906d66f931b721c0dbdb3","tid":141493,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T03:20:08.000Z","msg":"賤貨"},{"pid":"c598143d51482e113c1d89234e7753aa4c36ed4d","tid":141493,"uid":73441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T03:20:14.000Z","msg":"同我一齊啦"},{"pid":"026fddc993baabe1fe491b25efb2a0bd58f2cf97","tid":141493,"uid":12611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T03:20:27.000Z","msg":"咁你係呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf66c2e83b6b72a8feed9318d76eaa80ad0c347","tid":141493,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T03:22:15.000Z","msg":"咁你係雞呀嘛，比幾多男人屌過呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc822fb39ebe25852f1e57efb4c0d831bea4107","tid":141493,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T03:22:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賤貨</blockquote><br />\nYou竟然是個Cheap精"},{"pid":"e31caf43071c4c9c12369503767c71fcb4f40261","tid":141493,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T03:23:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同我一齊啦</blockquote><br />\nok pmed"},{"pid":"4a6059e94c9dc7443c27d6b43c3aac82a9401633","tid":14149